shows.title: #Roxy
shows.overview: When a girl falls for a hunky quarterback, her shy, but brainy friend conspires with the athlete to create a dream boy and woo her via social media.

shows.title: #Stuck
shows.overview: A hot one-night stand turns into an awkward morning after when GUY and HOLLY get STUCK in a dead-stopped traffic jam. As they begrudgingly get to know each other, we learn of their sexually raucous evening and then they're led to their surprising destiny.

shows.title: #Xmas
shows.overview: When interior designer, Jen, is selected for a social media competition for a design brand, she poses as an influencer with her best friend playing her husband and her nephew as her baby. Stars Clare Bowen and Brant Daugherty.

shows.title: Hashtag Prem
shows.overview: Sanika, a free-spirited girl, gets caught in the mist of love after she befriends JD online. To meet him, she travels to Goa, which changes her life forever.
When her husband is accused of taking part in an attempted military coup, a pregnant woman's life takes an emotional turn. Inspired by true events.

shows.title: 'Neath Brooklyn Bridge
shows.overview: Muggs and the East Side Kids come to the rescue of a wrongly-accused girl, who is discovered in the home of a man murdered by a mystery assailant.

shows.title: 'Twas the Text Before Christmas
shows.overview: An unexpected text message sent to the wrong number sets into motion a Christmas tradition with a new family over three separate years.

shows.title: (500) Days of Summer
shows.overview: In this anti- romantic comedy about love and fate, a young greeting card writer (Joseph Gordon-Levitt) is hopelessly, helplessly searching for the girl of his dreams...and his new co-worker, Summer Finn (Zooey Deschanel), may just be "the one." But the 500 days of their offbeat relationship reveal that the road to happiness can be unpredictable, uncontrollable and unbelievable.

shows.title: Kudrat
shows.overview: Kudrat is a 1981 romantic drama movie starring Rajesh Khanna, Hema Malini, Vinod Khanna, and Raaj Kumar. During her visit to Shimla, Chandramukhi meets Mohan and starts remembering incidents from her past life. She soon uncovers the mystery of her previous life and attempts to bring the culprit to justice.

shows.title: 1 Mile To You
shows.overview: Based on the novel “Life at These Speeds,” the moving story of a grieving teenager who reconciles his past and future through running.

shows.title: 1 Night
shows.overview: A generation gap of timeless truth unfolds as two couples, one in their thirties and the other are teens, explore love issues overnight at a hotel.
A Hollywood songwriter goes through a mid-life crisis and becomes infatuated with a sexy blond newlywed.

shows.title: 10 Reasons Why Men Cheat
shows.overview: In the wake of a wedding catastrophe, three couples unexpectedly discover the true meaning of commitment while brooding over one burning question.

shows.title: 10 Rules for Sleeping Around
shows.overview: An engaged couple seeking advice from happily married friends learns the secret to marital longevity is an open relationship dictated by ten rules.

shows.title: 10 Things I Hate About You
shows.overview: On the first day at his new school, Cameron instantly falls for Bianca the gorgeous girl of his dreams.

shows.title: 10 Things We Should Do Before We Break Up
shows.overview: Sparks fly when a self-sufficient single mom meets a magnetic perennial bachelor. On their first date, they collaborate--in jest--on the ultimate un-bucket list: ten things to do together before they break up. But when fate intervenes, this pair of cynics must embark on the most challenging journey of all, building a family together, and the chance to trade their cynicism for hope.
shows.originalTitle: 10 Things We Should Do Before We Break Up

shows.title: 10 Truths About Love
shows.overview: Carina writes relationship columns for a popular website and she’s known as an expert, but in real life love isn’t so easy.

shows.title: Teddy Bear
shows.overview: After failing to find love in Denmark, a painfully shy bodybuilder sets off for Thailand to escape from his overbearing mother and search for a bride.

shows.title: 10,000 Km
shows.overview: The long-term relationship between Barcelona natives Alex and Sergi is pushed to the limit when Alex gets a job 6,000 miles away in Los Angeles.

shows.title: 100 Girls
shows.overview: In this romantic comedy, a college student tries to to find the mysterious woman he connected with in an elevator during a campus blackout.
